
== Enki Scripts ==

Add a new entry to changelog.
Then run build process

% dch -i 
% make build

All files in subdirectoy 'bin' is mapped to enki/bin.
'scripts' is mapped to etc/enki/scripts



== Warning ==

Installing enki-scripts or updating the enki-scripts package
will restart the firewall. If the package is messed up it
could mess up any machine in which it is installed.


== check_files.rb ==

% ruby  check_files.rb
This reports on files which are missing from the package
file list files in debian/*.install .

